datasets.name: dataset_21
queryLines: SELECT `App Version` AS `App Version`, MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `App Version`) * 100 AS `% Active Devices By Appversion` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model` WHERE `App Version` NOT IN ('not a store release', 'other non-releases') AND `Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' AND `Os Version` IS NOT NULL ORDER BY `% Active Devices By Appversion` DESC

fields.name: % Active Devices By Appversion
fields.expression: MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `App Version`) * 100
